00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, justru setelah investigasi polisi,</font>

178
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,960
<font color=#FFFF00>dan diketahui dia saksi insiden masa lalu,
