179
00:13:38,890 --> 00:13:40,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa lagi alasan di balik semua ini?</font>

180
00:13:40,330 --> 00:13:43,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia  ingin bermain sampai akhir?</font>

181
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:47,160
