183
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dia meninggalkan catatan.</font>

184
00:13:51,890 --> 00:13:52,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

185
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa dia meninggalkan sebuah catatan?</i></font>

186
00:13:55,930 --> 00:13:59,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dan kenapa dia menujukan catatan
