961
01:03:36,140 --> 01:03:37,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kelihatannya ini lezat.</i></font>

962
01:03:37,410 --> 01:03:38,910
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Rasanya juga enak, tahu.</i></font>

963
01:03:43,240 --> 01:03:44,310
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau menyukainya?</i></font>

964
01:03:44,640 --> 01:03:46,740
